# Coffee Rating Application

## Description
A Flask-based web application where users can vote for coffee items and the vote count is stored in a database.

## Features
- Coffee Voting System
- Vote Count Updates
- SQLite Database Storage
- Flask Backend
- Interactive UI

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Flask
- SQLite
- HTML/CSS

## Installation

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run application:

python app.py
